the box model: properties:
- content
- padding: from box inside to text
- border
- margin: from box outside


BOOTSTRAP:
	- Bootstrap Min: la versio mnimitzada, treient tots els espais. Es el mateix que bootstrap.css

	- Bootstrap CDN (Content Delivery Network): si no ens voleu baixar l'arxiu, podem accedir a la versio hosted, nomes copiant el link


button {
height: 100%;} //takes 100 of all the div


//span takes 20% of the screen
span{
	display: inline-block;
	width: 20%;
}


transition: all 2.0s; // whenever ANY property changes, we transition in 2 scs it will take to secs to change the properties

transition: background 0.6s; //when background color changes, it will take 0.6 secs

SOMETIMES TRANSITIONS DOESNT WORK IN ALL BROWSERS SO WE HAVE TO SPECIFY:
	transition: background 0.6s;
	-webkit-transition: background 0.6s;
	-moz-transition:background 0.6s;


MARING
margin: 20px auto;  //is 20px in top and bottom and auto in left_-right (center)

